profile.yourself: I am Prince Mangal, and I am from Morena, Madhya Pradesh.I completed my B.Sc in the Science stream from Jiwaji University, Gwalior. As a Science student, Mathematics was my core subject, and also keen interest in solving logical & Mind math problems. Recently I did my five-month internship with Safilo India, which is the world's second-largest eyewear Manufacturing, Designing, & Distributing company. They are catering to luxury Eyewear Sunglasses & Frames.Apart from my internship, I Have done three different live projects in different sectors.
